title: Per Capita Personal Consumption Expenditures: Services: Household Consumption Expenditures for Services for Nevada
notes:
Personal consumption expenditures of a given area divided by the resident population of the area.

Consists of actual and imputed consumption expenditures for services by resident households.For more information about this release go to http://www.bea.gov/newsreleases/regional/pce/pce_newsrelease.htm.
